      <section eId="sec_SRULE-16-8">
        <num>SRULE 16.8</num>
        <heading>Section </heading>
        <subsection eId="SRULE-16-8__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The governor and each other appropriate official shall be notified of each appointment confirmed by the Senate no later than the day after the confirmation.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="SRULE-16-8__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Immediately after final adjournment of each session, the Secretary shall furnish to the governor or other official a list of any appointments submitted by any of them which were rejected or not confirmed.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=180486</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
